WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.002 --> 00:00:03.587
Thanks for coming,
everybody.

00:00:03.587 --> 00:00:05.172
I'm sure you all heard

00:00:05.172 --> 00:00:07.883
there was yet another
school shooting today.

00:00:07.883 --> 00:00:11.386
We have to figure out what
we're going to do as parents

00:00:11.386 --> 00:00:13.805
because this whole thing
is out of control.

00:00:13.805 --> 00:00:16.516
[ Sighs ]
We have to ask ourselves

00:00:16.516 --> 00:00:19.937
why this is happening
and do something now!

00:00:21.271 --> 00:00:22.689
Well, you know, Sharon,

00:00:22.689 --> 00:00:24.900
I think it is
a complex issue, you know.

00:00:24.900 --> 00:00:29.488
It's -- It's not really
as simple as just --

00:00:29.488 --> 00:00:32.115
What I'm saying is that --
that with issues like this,

00:00:32.115 --> 00:00:35.494
sometimes you have
to be kind of...crazy?

00:00:35.494 --> 00:00:37.746
What are you
talking about?!

00:00:37.746 --> 00:00:41.208
Do you understand that our
children are being murdered?

00:00:41.208 --> 00:00:42.584
Red.

00:00:42.584 --> 00:00:45.170
How much closer to home
can this all hit?

00:00:45.170 --> 00:00:47.547
It was at our
children's school!

00:00:47.547 --> 00:00:49.883
Crazy time.
Crazy red time.

00:00:51.969 --> 00:00:54.137
I agree with my wife.

00:00:54.137 --> 00:00:57.975
Well, there certainly are
things that need changing.

00:00:57.975 --> 00:01:00.686
Just yesterday, I was
at the park with my son Craig,

00:01:00.686 --> 00:01:03.522
and have you seen the state
of the playground equipment?

00:01:03.522 --> 00:01:05.607
Not only does it seem unsafe,

00:01:05.607 --> 00:01:07.693
but it's become quite
an eyesore.

00:01:07.693 --> 00:01:10.028
The whole park could use
an upgrade, if you ask me.

00:01:10.028 --> 00:01:11.780
It's become a camp-out
for the homeless.

00:01:11.780 --> 00:01:13.949
Are you [bleep] joking?!

00:01:13.949 --> 00:01:15.993
You're gonna take one second

00:01:15.993 --> 00:01:19.579
to compare child murder
to park upgrades?!

00:01:19.579 --> 00:01:21.832
What is wrong
with everybody?!

00:01:21.832 --> 00:01:23.834
You've all gone crazy!

00:01:28.213 --> 00:01:29.881
Anybody need a drink?

